# Color Admin Layout Rules

## Layout Structure

TheButler uses a **Color Admin-inspired** admin dashboard layout:

```html
<div class="app-layout">
  <app-sidebar />      <!-- Fixed left, 250px wide -->
  <div class="app-content">
    <app-topbar />     <!-- Fixed top, 60px height -->
    <main class="main-content">
      <router-outlet />
    </main>
  </div>
</div>
```

Reference: [app.html](mdc:src/app/app.html), [app.scss](mdc:src/app/app.scss)

## Sidebar Specifications

**File**: [sidebar component](mdc:src/app/shared/sidebar/)

- **Width**: 250px (collapsed: 60px)
- **Background**: #2d353c (gray-800 from Color Admin)
- **Position**: Fixed, top: 0, bottom: 0, left: 0
- **Z-index**: 1020
- **Padding-top**: 60px (for topbar clearance)

### Profile Section
- Avatar: 60px circle
- Background: #242a30 with pattern overlay
- User name + role display
- Positioned at top after topbar

### Menu Items
- **Active state**: Gold left border (3px) + gold text + light gold background
- **Hover**: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)` background
- **Icon width**: 35px, centered
- **Font size**: 13.5px
- **Padding**: 12px 20px
- **Badge**: Gold background, charcoal text

### Menu Header
- **Text**: "Navigation" (uppercase)
- **Font size**: 11px
- **Color**: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)`
- **Padding**: 12px 20px 8px

### Minify Button
- Positioned at bottom
- Border-top: 1px solid `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)`
- Toggles sidebar width

## Topbar Specifications

**File**: [topbar component](mdc:src/app/shared/topbar/)

- **Height**: 60px
- **Background**: White
- **Shadow**: `0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)`
- **Position**: Fixed, top: 0, left: 0, right: 0
- **Z-index**: 1010

### Brand Section (Left)
- **Width**: 250px (matches sidebar)
- **Background**: #2d353c (matches sidebar)
- **Logo**: Butler icon + "TheButler" text
- **Font**: Light weight for name

### Search Bar (Center)
- **Width**: Max 300px, flexible
- **Padding**: 8px 40px 8px 15px
- **Border-radius**: 6px
- **Background**: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02)`
- **Focus**: Expands to 120%, gold border

### Right Actions
- **Notification Icon**: Bell with count badge
- **User Avatar**: 36px circle
- **Dropdowns**: Click-away behavior with `stopPropagation`

### Dropdown Styling
- **Width**: Notifications: 360px, Profile: 240px
- **Shadow**: `0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)`
- **Animation**: Slide down (0.2s)
- **Border-radius**: 6px

## Main Content Specifications

**File**: [app.scss](mdc:src/app/app.scss)

- **Margin-left**: 250px (for sidebar)
- **Margin-top**: 60px (for topbar)
- **Padding**: 20px 25px
- **Background**: #f2f3f4 (Color Admin light gray)
- **Min-height**: `calc(100vh - 60px)`

## Page Structure Pattern

Every page should follow this structure:

```html
<div class="page-name">
  <app-breadcrumb [items]="breadcrumbs" />
  <h1 class="page-header">Page Title</h1>
  
  <!-- Page content -->
</div>
```

### Breadcrumbs
- **Component**: [breadcrumb](mdc:src/app/shared/breadcrumb/)
- **Position**: Float right
- **Font size**: 12px
- **Color**: Gray with gold hover
- **Separator**: `/`

### Page Header
- **Font size**: 28px
- **Font weight**: 300 (light)
- **Line height**: 40px
- **Color**: #242a30
- **Margin-bottom**: 25px
- **Display**: Flex with space-between for action buttons

## Card Components

- **Background**: White
- **Border**: None
- **Border-radius**: 6px
- **Shadow**: `0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)`
- **Hover shadow**: `0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)`
- **Margin-bottom**: 15px

### Card Header
- **Padding**: 20px
- **Border-bottom**: 1px solid `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)`
- **Font size**: 16px
- **Font weight**: 600

### Card Content
- **Padding**: 20px

### Card Variants
- `card--dark`: Background #2d353c
- `card--accent`: Butler gradient for special cards

## Spacing System

Match Color Admin's spacing:
- **Grid gaps**: 15px
- **Card margins**: 15px bottom
- **Section margins**: 20px
- **Content padding**: 20-25px
- **Form spacing**: 20px between fields

## Responsive Breakpoints

### Mobile (< 768px)
- Sidebar: Transform off-screen
- Topbar brand: Auto width
- Search: Hidden
- User name: Hidden
- Content: Padding 15px
- Buttons: Full width stacked

## Color Variables from Color Admin

- **Sidebar BG**: #2d353c
- **Sidebar Darker**: #242a30
- **Content BG**: #f2f3f4
- **Card BG**: #ffffff
- **Text Dark**: #242a30
- **Text Gray**: #666
- **Border**: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05-0.1)`

## Butler Theme Overrides

While matching Color Admin structure, maintain butler identity:
- **Accent**: #d4af37 (gold) instead of #348fe2 (blue)
- **Primary**: #1a1a2e (charcoal) for dark elements
- **Active states**: Gold highlighting
- **Badges**: Gold background
